sparql_query_kg2:
Based on the provided information, I will generate the SPARQL query for DBpedia.

Wikidata query:
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?val 
WHERE {  <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2608065> <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P2130> ?val }

ER2 mapping:
[
  {
    "dbpedia_id": "http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Lego_Movie",
    "wikidata_ids": [
      "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2608065"
    ]
  },
  {
    "dbpedia_id": "http://dbpedia.org/ontology/budget",
    "wikidata_ids": [
      "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/P2769"
    ]
  }
]

DBpedia query:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
SELECT ?budget
WHERE { ?movie dbo:film ?budget 
        FILTER (regex(str(?movie), "The Lego Movie"))
        FILTER (regex(str(?budget), "€")) }

