PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?uri
WHERE {
  ?uri dbo:birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna> .
  ?uri dbo:deathPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin> .
}
</sparql>
```

However, this query doesn't match the original Wikidata query's complexity and logic. To achieve the same result, we can use a more complex query, similar to the original Wikidata query:

```sparql
